OL,3,CPlans for Stonehenge road tunnel
OL,4,Cofficially scrapped
OL,6,FPlans to build a road tunnel near
OL,7,FStonehenge have been officially
OL,8,Fscrapped by the government.
OL,10,FThe Transport Secretary's decision to
OL,11,Frevoke planning consent brings an end
OL,12,Fto the long-running proposal to
OL,13,Fupgrade the A303 between Amesbury and
OL,14,FBerwick Down.
OL,16,FThe Government had originally approved
OL,17,Fthe the A303 project in 2023.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
