OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773947499
OL,3,CPlans for Stonehenge road tunnel
OL,4,Cofficially scrapped
OL,6,FThe Department for Transport (DfT)
OL,7,Fsaid that "exceptional circumstances"
OL,8,Fhave led it to revoke the development
OL,9,Fconsent order, which would have seen a
OL,10,Ftunnel, two junctions and a northern
OL,11,Fbypass built close to the world
OL,12,Fheritage site.
OL,14,FIf the plans were to be revived in
OL,15,Ffuture, the revocation means that the
OL,16,Fapplicant would have to apply again
OL,17,Ffrom scratch.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
