CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773947499
OL,3,CPlans for Stonehenge road tunnel
OL,4,Cofficially scrapped
OL,6,FRachel Reeves said the Conservatives
OL,7,Foverspent by billions of pounds after
OL,8,Fmaking a series of "unfunded
OL,9,Fcommitments".
OL,11,FShe said there is a #22 billion hole
OL,12,Fin the public finances, which she
OL,13,Ffirmly blamed on the former
OL,14,FConservative government.
OL,16,FWiltshire Council previously expressed
OL,17,Fits disappointment at the announcement.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
