CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773947499
OL,3,CPlans for Stonehenge road tunnel
OL,4,Cofficially scrapped
OL,6,FCllr Richard Clewer, Leader of
OL,7,FWiltshire Council, said: "We are
OL,8,Fextremely dismayed and disappointed at
OL,9,Fthe Government's decision to cancel
OL,10,Fthe A303 Stonehenge tunnel project.
OL,12,F"These improvements are needed now to
OL,13,Fease traffic congestion on the A303
OL,14,Fand reduce traffic in our communities,
OL,15,Fand also ensure economic growth in
OL,16,FWiltshire, unlocking jobs and
OL,17,Finvestment in the wider south-west
OL,18,Fregion.
OL,26,@oD@ZOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
