FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1773947499
OL,3,CPlans for Stonehenge road tunnel
OL,4,Cofficially scrapped
OL,6,F"It has taken many years of lobbying
OL,7,Fand working closely with partners,
OL,8,Fincluding National Highways, to bring
OL,9,Fthis major infrastructure project to
OL,10,FWiltshire, and so it is a huge blow to
OL,11,Fget to the stage when construction is
OL,12,Fready to begin, only to have this
OL,13,Ftaken away from us at this late hour."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
